    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment is accepted. The majority of credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The Test conditions factor was identified as below the required level; however, the assessment team determined that the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol is the accepted regulatory standard for this device class and that the deficit does not materially affect the fitness-for-purpose conclusion. The Output comparison and associated factors were reviewed and found to support the acceptance decision.",
